author: Reuters Editorial
title: BRIEF-Five9 Reports Q4 Earnings Per Share $0.07
text:
Feb 21 (Reuters) - Five9 Inc:
* FIVE9 REPORTS RECORD ANNUAL REVENUE OF $200 MILLION, UP 24% YEAR-OVER-YEAR
* Q4 NON-GAAP EARNINGS PER SHARE $0.07
* Q4 REVENUE ROSE 25 PERCENT TO $55.4 MILLION * SEES FY 2018 NON-GAAP EARNINGS PER SHARE $0.20 TO $0.25
* SEES FY 2018 REVENUE $231 MILLION TO $234 MILLION * SEES Q1 2018 REVENUE $54.5 MILLION TO $55.5 MILLION * Q4 GAAP LOSS PER SHARE $0.01 * SEES FY 2018 GAAP NET LOSS OF $0.23 TO $0.18 PER BASIC SHARE
* SEES Q1 2018 GAAP NET LOSS OF $0.08 TO $0.06 PER BASIC SHARE
* SEES Q1 2018 ADJUSTED EARNINGS PER SHARE OF $0.02 TO $0.04
* Q4 EARNINGS PER SHARE VIEW $0.04, REVENUE VIEW $52.3 MILLION -- THOMSON REUTERS I/B/E/S
* FY2018 REVENUE VIEW $231.4 MILLION -- THOMSON REUTERS I/B/E/S
* Q1 EARNINGS PER SHARE VIEW $0.01, REVENUE VIEW $54.9 MILLION -- THOMSON REUTERS I/B/E/S Source text for Eikon: Further company coverage:
